<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Alpha Animals</li>
    </mods>
    <nomatch Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Leather_Chitin"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>키틴질</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Leather_Chitin"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>곤충의 키틴질이 단단한 비늘처럼 겹쳐져 있습니다. 전투에서는 매우 튼튼하지만 날씨로부터는 거의 보호해 주지 못합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </nomatch>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Biotech</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
      <mods>
        <li>lla Animals Expanded — Waste Animals</li>
      </mods>
      <nomatch Class="PatchOperationSequence">
        <success>Always</success>
        <operations>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VAEWaste_ToxicLeather"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>폐기물 가죽</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VAEWaste_ToxicLeather"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>쉽게 벗겨지는 저품질의 짙은 녹갈색 가죽입니다. 불이 매우 잘 붙습니다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="ToxicMeat"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>독성 고기</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="ToxicMeat"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>독성 동물에게서 얻은 생고기입니다.\n\n질기고 젤라틴 같으며 역겹습니다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThoughtDef[defName="AteToxicMeatDirect"]/stages/li[1]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>독성 고기를 먹음</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThoughtDef[defName="AteToxicMeatDirect"]/stages/li[1]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>독성 고기를 먹었다. 아마 내가 지금껏 맛본 것 중 가장 역겨운 음식이었을 것이다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThoughtDef[defName="AteToxicMeatAsIngredient"]/stages/li[1]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>조리된 독성 고기를 먹음</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/ThoughtDef[defName="AteToxicMeatAsIngredient"]/stages/li[1]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>독성 고기로 만든 음식을 먹었다. 양념이 맛을 어느 정도 가려 주었지만, 여전히 독이 든 듯한 맛이 났다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
        </operations>
      </nomatch>
    </match>
  </Operation>
